{"tid":770623,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我既夢想職業係家庭主婦","createTime":"2018-08-07T09:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T16:02:34.000Z","uid":32263,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7734f50c296e1547e6ec98267adf3a622747f513","tid":770623,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"可以點樣入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日晾衫洗衫<br />\n下妟四點食個吉野家下午茶<br />\n同c9吹下買咩抵<br />\nDyson吸塵機出到咩型號<br />\n六點鐘炒個肉碌個菜有心情滾個湯<br />\n夜晚睇陣電視，上床剝定衫俾人扑<br />\n<br />\n完美生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7222f3b5f87cbef24c9a9a7c3e8453acb0912152","tid":770623,"uid":179292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"嫁注好人家。"},{"pid":"bab43857c9bdd5c276b8fe832a00ede95fb97aed","tid":770623,"uid":33147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做乜師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6524e0592a0d47c69b1484215debd83f7ad1f411","tid":770623,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"你家姐想做歌手？"},{"pid":"b9b389be7547a3a2c0748b24ed9ae4f05d53c977","tid":770623,"uid":66701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n不過無講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朝早送小b 同老公返學返工<br />\n然後自摺睇新聞/股市食個靚早餐<br />\n下午做住電影台睇同一邊做家務，晏晝出去食個tea同買定餸<br />\n湊住b煮飯等老公番來食飯，<br />\n等老公食飯沖涼個時同bb 狂玩然後等b訓得好唸就再夜晚準備扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6177baf7e70ca993b277aa9ceb2a303bba8901","tid":770623,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab43857c9bdd5c276b8fe832a00ede95fb97aed","tid":770623,"uid":33147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做乜師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g